%N A015366 Inverse of 1357th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015366 Periodic with period length 1357. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015366 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015366/b015366.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015366 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1357.
%H A015366 <a href="/index/Rec#order_1276">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 1276.
%H A015366 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015366 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A015366 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[1357,x],{x,0,120}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Apr 21 2022 *)
%o A015366 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1357)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
